/w26/newsletter-2026-w26.html"],"type":"attachment"},"06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.html":{"title":"HK3hduDagAAaoGI","icon":"","description":"<img src=\"06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.jpg\" target=\"_self\">","aliases":[],"inlineTags":[],"frontmatterTags":[],"headers":[],"links":[],"author":"","coverImageURL":".","fullURL":"06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.html","pathToRoot":"../..","attachments":["06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.html"],"createdTime":1782568414062,"modifiedTime":1782568414062,"sourceSize":98268,"sourcePath":"06 newsletter/w26/HK3hduDagAAaoGI.jpg","exportPath":"06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.html","showInTree":true,"treeOrder":11,"backlinks":["06-newsletter/w26/newsletter-2026-w26.html"],"type":"attachment"},"06-newsletter/w26/newsletter-2026-w26.html":{"title":"newsletter-2026-W26","icon":"","description":"A curation of ideas, memes and media which would which would have cluttered the chat too much.Now a lot of things might seem irrelevant or out of them blue, that's cause I'm gonna be sending it to several people.\nI'm planning to do this instead of being constantly active on whatsapp/insta.\nIf you have not interacted with a particular piece of media, beware of potential spoilers.I wanted to include my rant about how both sides of communism and capitalism debate and my annoyances with them in here, but it turned out to be waaay too long. I will be writing a blog post on it probably.\nI will be finished with it after I am done doing a 100% run of papers, please.\n<img alt=\"4h0364qnzn8h1.jpeg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/4h0364qnzn8h1.jpeg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 200px; max-width: 100%;\">let's get onto it.Tadc ended. It was great show which deserved a better ending in my opinion, but these types of endings are what fuel really good fanfics.<br>\n<img alt=\"Pasted image 20260627193700.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260627193700.png\" target=\"_self\">\nAn obligatory \"fuck you\" to gooseworx. No way it had been planned since 2016 😭.throw in the dysfunctional canon family in the wild and you're gonna get ratioed by wholesome fanfics and fanarts.<br>\n<img alt=\"HEzae_QacAEwCMe.png\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/hezae_qacaewcme.png\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 500px; max-width: 100%;\"><br><img alt=\"Gv5-uJwXUAAOxoz.jpg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/gv5-ujwxuaaoxoz.jpg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 300px; max-width: 100%;\"><br><img alt=\"HK3hduDagAAaoGI.jpg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.jpg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 300px; max-width: 100%;\"><br>\n<img alt=\"8xfim00w8d6h1.jpeg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/8xfim00w8d6h1.jpeg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 300px; max-width: 100%;\"><br><img alt=\"ytz2ubdj8w8h1.png\" src=\"ytz2ubdj8w8h1.png\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 300px; max-width: 100%;\">\nRadical centrist stalin<br><img alt=\"HJMbXLeWwAA-etT.jpg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/hjmbxlewwaa-ett.jpg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 400px; max-width: 100%;\">\nclassic horseshoe. <br><img alt=\"HH3vbR8aoAAG-ka.jpg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/hh3vbr8aoaag-ka.jpg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 400px; max-width: 100%;\">\nThis one had been pretty popular.\nNot sure about the other quadrants, but going with the common libright theory, as long as the state stays out of it, unions are not a problem. The main issue is when you have state mandated unions which cause issues.\nI have not found people with the given \"opposite\" beliefs yet. I'll let you interpret this one on your own lol.<br>\n<img alt=\"h0d1vl8wyn8h1.jpeg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/h0d1vl8wyn8h1.jpeg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 300px; max-width: 100%;\">Saw someone describe themselves as neurospicy, and now I can't not think of that whenever I think about neurodivergence.<br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260627193833.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260627193833.png\" target=\"_self\">\nClassic reddit moment. The top two posts. <br><img alt=\"Pasted image 20260627194037.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260627194037.png\" target=\"_self\">\n🙂<br><img alt=\"1unp0g930dsg1.jpeg\" src=\"06-newsletter/w26/1unp0g930dsg1.jpeg\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 400px; max-width: 100%;\">\nThis is blatant misinformation. My socks are actually longer than shown in the figure. (/s obviously 😭)\nI can cook paneer relatively consistently, and I seem to be happy with the results. the pic below of an unfinished attempt is the only one I could find.<br>\n<img alt=\"Pasted image 20260627194214.png\" src=\"pasted-image-20260627194214.png\" target=\"_self\" style=\"width: 600px; max-width: 100%;\">My ps1 internship station has not contacted in more than a week now. Atp, as long as I get free marks I do not care.This was a kind of a pilot thingy which I am sending to people who may potentially like this stuff. I will likely be sending this every week?","aliases":[],"inlineTags":[],"frontmatterTags":[],"headers":[{"heading":"Media","level":1,"id":"Media_0"},{"heading":"Tadc","level":2,"id":"Tadc_0"},{"heading":"tcoaal.","level":2,"id":"tcoaal._0"},{"heading":"ddlc","level":2,"id":"ddlc_0"},{"heading":"political stuff","level":1,"id":"political_stuff_0"},{"heading":"misc","level":1,"id":"misc_0"},{"heading":"life updates","level":1,"id":"life_updates_0"}],"links":[],"author":"","coverImageURL":".","fullURL":"06-newsletter/w26/newsletter-2026-w26.html","pathToRoot":"../..","attachments":["06-newsletter/w26/4h0364qnzn8h1.html","pasted-image-20260627193700.png","06-newsletter/w26/hezae_qacaewcme.html","06-newsletter/w26/gv5-ujwxuaaoxoz.html","06-newsletter/w26/hk3hdudagaaaogi.html","06-newsletter/w26/8xfim00w8d6h1.html","ytz2ubdj8w8h1.png","06-newsletter/w26/hjmbxlewwaa-ett.html","06-newsletter/w26/hh3vbr8aoaag-ka.html","06-newsletter/w26/h0d1vl8wyn8h1.html","pasted-image-20260627193833.png","pasted-image-20260627194037.png","06-newsletter/w26/1unp0g930dsg1.html","pasted-image-20260627194214.png"],"createdTime":1782567847967,"modifiedTime":1782574661605,"sourceSize":2705,"sourcePath":"06 newsletter/w26/newsletter-